##Honey, we'll be back after we catch the monster

Story exercise

Verse 65

Xiaojinzi is the same year and I came to work in the entry and exit health check center, tall, she has a beautiful soft baby face, smile eyes crooked. Her family name is Kim, we all affectionately call her little gold, it seems not so called on her lovely. In a battle that has become increasingly contentious, COVID-19 and her husband at the CDC, Xiao Yang, have had the most direct, face to face contact with the virus, the following story is based on the narration of Little Gold.

-1-

Xiao Yang and I are both medical students. Xiao Yang works at the Xi'an Center for Disease Control and Prevention, a unit that many people remember from the SARS epidemic in 2003.

Soon after marrying Xiaoyang, I felt the particularity of his work. His phone is rarely off, whether it is eating, or in the middle of the night, he often received a call from the office, many times he would hastily put a sentence, "something to come, I went to the office. "

It could be one night, it could be two or three days. Gradually, my daughter got used to it, and I would tell her, "daddy's gone to catch the little monster. " She grinned. "Is Daddy Ultraman? "

In her daughter's naive world, she would think of her father as a superhero fighting monsters with a sword. In fact, Dad was just sitting in his lab wearing a thick hazmat suit, trying to pick up traces of the virus from sample after sample, the tiny, cunning virus that would kill countless people without a sound, h1N1 swine flu, H7N9 AVIAN FLU..

When I describe all this to my colleagues, they often open their mouths wide in surprise. "Oh, it's like on TV, you say you have a job, you go out, you don't see anyone for days. "

I laugh, I am also a medical student, deeply aware that, involving life, all delays and hesitation, even if it is only a minute, may cause irreparable pain and regret, so I understand.

Worried? To be honest, there will be some. However, I also work in the entry-exit medical examination center, all day to face is also a blood, body fluid samples, because understand, so not too panic.

But this time, I was a little worried, from the New Year's Eve, nearly a month, I can only see him in the news photos. I could see his eyes all over the camera, but I could spot him out in the crowd.

-2-

We began to pay attention to this epidemic in mid-january, but never imagined that it would take only three days from "limited human-to-human transmission" to the closure of Wuhan, a thoroughfare in nine provinces with a population of more than 10 million.

January 24, New Year's Eve, our family is ready to eat a meal together, Xiaoyang Work Group constantly pop up information. Because of the rapid spread of the epidemic, the center set up a prevention and Control Emergency Response Team, and the initial preparation of the list of prevention and control personnel.

Wechat group, everyone have replied: "I have arrived at the post" "45 minutes to arrive" "I am not in the list, need to call me at any time, 30 minutes to arrive" .

Xiaoyang was on the list. He looked at me apologetically. Without waiting for him to explain anything more, I immediately said: "You go, two children have me, have parents. "

The eldest daughter is in the second grade and has become sensible. She is reluctant to give up looking at her father. The younger daughter is innocently holding Xiaoyang's hand and pointing to the dishes on the table. "Daddy, have dinner. " Xiaoyang gently pulls her hand out of her daughter's hand and touches her hair, "Be good, father went to catch a small monster. " Then went out.

When he went, there was no news for several days.

Afterwards I just know, that same evening, small Yang went to the 8th hospital to sample for the patient. The Eighth Hospital, an Infectious Disease Hospital, was a designated hospital in Xi'an during the SARS epidemic in 2003, making many people afraid to hear its name. Today, this is the most common place for new coronary pneumonia.

An important indicator of the diagnosis of NCP is whether the viral nucleic acid test in the nasopharyngeal swab is positive or not. In the process of collecting a nasopharyngeal Swab, Xiao Yang needs to make face-to-face contact with the subject and stick a cotton swab into his nose and throat to collect samples. Specifications and standards for the entire collection process are critical, and if the depth is not deep enough, it is possible that the virus can not be detected because the sample is not up to scratch. Coughing, sneezing, and even retching reactions are common when samples are taken. The resulting spray can splatter on the face masks and protective clothing of collectors and can easily become infected if not adequately protected.

I don't know if it was because of the cold or because of the tension, but on the night I went to take the swabs for the suspected patient, Xiaoyang developed gastrointestinal discomfort, cough, fatigue and other symptoms, which were highly consistent with the symptoms of the new pneumonia. He didn't dare tell me. He took his own medicine and rested for hours in a quarantined hotel.

In fact, the situation at that time did not allow him to think much, to undertake a lot of work, including pathogen detection, elimination, circulation, comprehensive coordination, material security. Although there are groups of people, each group is understaffed, and one person may have to take on several tasks, arranged in 12-hour shifts, but in fact, there is no rest time at all, even when lying in a hotel room, he's got a cell phone in his hand. He'll be here any minute if there's a call.

On the third night after leaving home, Xiao Yang made a video with me. Two daughters to the Mobile Phone Call Dad, he even said a word of strength is not, I see wrong, "pressed" for a long time, he na NA NA to say the body unwell things.

"How so? There is not comfortable rest can not rest for a while? You look like this. " I said angrily.

"No, I'm almost done, my temperature is normal, and I don't look well because I haven't slept much in the past few days, and, uh, I didn't sleep last night. "

"You... " I was so angry that I couldn't speak.

Xiaoyang see busy ingratiating said: "that, right away, I was divided in the laboratory, only testing, do not go out to run, time is also regular, can rest. "

I didn't have the heart to scold him. I said a few words and sent him to bed.

Actually, he didn't sleep that night, but he didn't tell me about it this time. I saw it on the news. Shortly after speaking with me, he went into the lab and began testing for a virus, or "catching the little monster, " as his daughter called it.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
-3-

Indeed, viral nucleic acid testing, much like catching a small monster, requires patience, skill and, above all, courage.

The form of the virus is so small that it can not be seen under an ordinary optical microscope, much less directly observed by the naked eye. But each virus has its own unique genetic sequence, and by detecting the viral nucleic acid in a patient's body, you can tell if the virus is present in the patient's body.

In the lab, Xiao Yang works with a set of nasal swabs. The swabs are dipped into a tube of virus samples, which are then split, separated and eluted using a kit to extract viral RNA, they were then added to the new coronaviruses and tested for the virus by real-time Quantitative PCR.

Virus detection, need to be meticulous and meticulous, especially the new crown virus this new infectious virus, one step careless, these crafty little things may be hidden away. People who carry the virus in their bodies, but it's not detected, become a moving source of infection. But at the same time, in the detection process, a little careless, will cause the virus aerosol spill, the need to strictly operate in accordance with the norms in the Biosafety cabinet, very dangerous.

On the night of January 27, I saw Xiaoyang on the Shaanxi News. I pointed to the figure and said, "Look, Dad. "

The little girl looked at him and shook her head. "No, he's not the father. "

The eldest daughter bit her finger and whispered, "why does daddy cover his face so tightly? I want to see him. I Miss Him. "

The next night, Xiaoyang and I talked on the phone, did not say a few words to start coughing. Before I could say anything, he explained, "it's OK, it's because I haven't had any water all day, so my throat itches. " He told me that there weren't enough protective clothing to go to the bathroom or eat or drink water, the body's protective clothing on the scrap, so they all agreed to a tacit understanding, work as far as possible do not eat, do not drink, do not go to the toilet.

"Actually, I'm in trouble. It takes half an hour to take off the equipment and half an hour to put it on. I might as well make more samples in that time. " "The center has taken care of the lab, " he said. "It has ensured that our protective clothing is supplied, and the colleagues who lost their group are much less likely to wear protective clothing than we are. " Although the group does not participate in laboratory testing, but they often come into contact with suspected patients, and the risk is high.

"The dragon of the whole village gave us the hardest scales, so of course we have to save some... it's OK, I'm wearing a protective suit and I'm very focused. I don't feel hungry or thirsty, " he said with a laugh.

-4-

Since January 28, the number of new confirmed and suspected cases in Xi'an has exceeded double digits daily, which means Xiaoyang and his team have a heavier task. Every confirmed or suspected case requires a great deal of work. In addition to sampling and testing, efforts are needed to identify the source of infection, map the patient's movements, where he or she went, who he or she came into contact with, and excavate close contacts, and disinfect the place where the patient was. All of this sounds like trivial work that needs to be done little by little.

Most of Xiaoyang's units are master's degree students in their 30s. Although the work is really hard, they are always happy, in the Work Group's painting style is often: "The 12th team receives the order, the 13th team prepares" "The big job, 10-20th team prepares to receive the order" "the list arrives where, when only arrives 23rd team" "last night that order, I ran until 2 o'clock in the morning" ... they call the task "single" , goes out the work calls "to appear" , the wechat group name has also changed from the serious "flow Adjustment Group" , "disinfector group" to the mischievous lovely "small flying team" .

January 31 at 9:00 pm, the command congratulates you, "today's single party. " Everyone replied: "worried about the midnight mission I cry with joy. ".

Xiaoyang is also happy to return to the isolation hotel to rest, I took advantage of his good mood, weakly told him on the phone: "that, I also began to work these days, the sample of suspected immigration. "

Small Yang One Leng, say: "I this all the time can't go home, how do you also want to enter the laboratory to test this? "

I said half-jokingly, "I will screen out all the suspects for you first. Won't that reduce your workload? "

He was silent for a moment and said four words, "be careful. "

In fact, as early as the evening of January 27, I received a notice to do nucleic acid screening of fever passengers in the entry and exit personnel, the next morning, I set out. At that time, many of the buses in Xi'an had been closed, and the ones that didn't were every hour. It was not practical to take buses, and there were almost no taxis and so on. Before Xiaoyang at home can drive me to work, now there is no driver's license I can only choose to ride a shared bike.

It's six kilometers from home to work and takes about 40 minutes to cycle all the way. Usually, the second ring is like a tree whose leaves are blown off by the autumn wind. It is bare. There is no one or a car except me. All along the road, the front rooms were pasted with bright red couplets and hung with big red lanterns, but the doors were closed tightly. "It's like the whole world has been driven home by a virus, " I said to myself, trying to break the suffocating silence by humming through my mask as I pedaled furiously.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
-5-

On the afternoon of February 2, a colleague forwarded an official document, which mentioned that four laboratory staff members of Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital, who had no direct contact with patients, had contracted new coronary pneumonia, some speculate that the patient's sample formed aerosols in the air. At this point, the possibility that aerosols can cause infection has been taken into account, however, at the expense of four testers.

Since starting work on New Year's Eve, Xiaoyang has only been shuttling back and forth between hotels and workplaces. Due to heavy work and irregular rest, almost all of them have symptoms of discomfort. They don't go home for work, it is also in case of misfortune, "caught" oneself will not become a source of infection. While I was at work, I also tried not to contact my family and kept to myself in a small room.

Both daughters wanted to play with me, and my mother coaxed them softly outside. "Be good, Mommy's gone to catch the little monster, too, and she needs rest when she's tired. " The older daughter urged the younger daughter, "they'll catch it faster if they catch it together. " The mother laughed.

Since I and Xiaoyang go to work, the two children are handed over to the mother, she side inside and outside hard, while worrying for us.

I tried to ask my mother, there is no regret for me to learn medicine, she smiled, "I also participated in the fight against SARS AH. "

It occurred to me that 17 years ago, when I was in college, my mother had been drafted into the epidemic response unit as a technical cadre, wearing protective clothing all day long and unable to communicate with her family. I carry IC card downstairs to call my mother, the ear that nobody answered the Empty Empty Ring, let me have unspeakable horror.

"were you afraid, mother? " I asked.

Mother thought for a moment, answered: "Afraid, of course afraid, but if even we are not on, then who can block in front of the virus? " Pause for a moment, she said: "You and Xiaoyang to work, have your mother when you good logistics. "

17 years later, I and Xiaoyang also made the same choice and mother that year, but the people concerned and the people concerned about the swap, however, concerned about the mind is the same.

On Feb. 5, my Alma Mater, the Dalian Medical University, set out in full gear, many of whom I knew well, and none of whom, I think, had broken their vows to practice medicine at the time.

On February 8, when I got home, there was a picture taped to the door of my small room, painted by my eldest daughter. The small sun wearing white protective clothing, awe-inspiring, after his own seven-color Halo, rolling his eyes of coronavirus was beaten by him without the slightest ability to fight back. Next to a big Red Heart, wrote: "Dad to fight the monster, has been many, many days did not go home, Dad, I miss you! "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The first daughter's picture on the door

Since February 21, the province cleared of suspected cases, that is, since that day, Shaanxi new coronary pneumonia cases have been confirmed to zero. This is great news for us. Xiaoyang said, so that the new cases of zero for 28 days in a row, he can come back, the two girls arm fingers, a day to count, "how many days, we can see the father. "

Unexpectedly, the prevention of imported cases became a new problem in early March, with a worldwide outbreak of the new form of coronary pneumonia and a sharp increase in the number of returnees. The bulk of the samples were sent to my lab, where the lab staff are on call 24 hours a day. Xiaoyang said jokingly: "play the first half, and the second half, this time you are the main. " However, watching can come back to him, the time to go home again can not be expected.

On March 15, I arrived at the lab at 10 p.m. , and when I finished taking the samples from the airport, it was already 6 a.m. , when I pulled off my protective clothing, stretched my numb body, and thought of my little daughter's question to her sister, "Isn't daddy coming back? Why is the little monster always catching. " The eldest daughter comforted her: "They are so hard to catch, soon, soon. "

I smiled as I watched the sun rise in the east. I believed that we would win in the end. We had to protect this land because there were people we loved.

-END-
